comments: Flynn (TOR) maintains a rested hand on Irving's (BKN) side and marginal contact occurs as Irving drives inside the perimeter.
Irving (BKN) goes to, not through, Flynn (TOR) and marginal contact occurs as they come together inside the lane at the end of Irving's drive.
Flynn (TOR) legally contests Irving's (BKN) jump shot attempt.
Barnes (TOR) releases the inbound prior to his right foot landing.
Durant (BKN) engages and disengages with Siakam (TOR) as Siakam moves to set the pick.
Simmons (BKN) engages and disengages with Siakam (TOR) as they go over the screen.
Durant (BKN) turns alongside Barnes' (TOR) path and marginal body contact occurs during Barnes' drive.
Durant (BKN) brings his left arm forward and initiates contact with Barnes' (TOR) right arm during Barnes' upward shooting motion.
Siakam (TOR) and Irving (BKN) engage and disengage with one another as the pick is set.
Barnes (TOR) is moving alongside Durant's (BKN) path and marginal body contact occurs during Durant's drive.
VanVleet (TOR) initiates contact with Durant's (BKN) right forearm during his upward shooting motion and affects Durant's jump shot attempt.
Siakam (TOR) brings his left hand forward and marginal contact occurs with Irving's (BKN) back as Irving elevates to pursue the rebound.
Siakam (TOR) re-establishes slightly following the initial contact with Watanabe (BKN), and further marginal contact occurs as they each engage and disengage with one another.
Barnes (TOR) jumps toward the basket as he defends the driving shot attempt and marginal contact occurs with Irving's (BKN) slightly extended off-arm.
Irving (BKN) brings his off-arm outward slightly and marginal contact occurs with Barnes' (TOR) front as Barnes defends the driving shot attempt.
Watanabe (BKN) is moving alongside Barnes' (TOR) path and absorbs the marginal body contact as Barnes spins toward the lane during the drive.
Watanabe (BKN) maintains verticality and absorbs the marginal body contact that occurs after Barnes' (TOR) gather. Durant (BKN) legally contests Barnes' driving shot attempt.
VanVleet (TOR) engages and disengages with Irving (BKN) off-ball.
VanVleet (TOR) moves forward slightly and brings his arm toward Durant's (BKN) path prior to marginal contact occurring with Durant's side/front near midcourt.

Irving (BKN) establishes himself in Siakam's (TOR) path and turns slightly prior to the marginal contact occurring simultaneously to the defensive switch. Irving and Siakam briefly engage and disengage thereafter.

VanVleet (TOR) brings his left arm toward Irving (BKN) and marginal contact occurs with Irving's front as he receives the pass. Flynn (TOR) moves forward slightly as he defends the pass and marginal contact occurs with Irving's back/side.
Barnes (TOR) jumps vertically and absorbs the marginal body contact that occurs at the end of Irving's (BKN) drive.
Irving (BKN) goes to, not through, Barnes' (TOR) space and marginal contact occurs at the end of Irving's drive.
VanVleet (TOR) establishes himself in Claxton's (BKN) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Siakam (TOR) and Durant (BKN) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.

Irving (BKN) turns and initiates body contact with Barnes (TOR) after his gather. After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor of a defensive goaltending by Durant (BKN) is overturned and the basket is not scored.
VanVleet (TOR) commits a take foul on Irving (BKN).
Durant (BKN) is firming up over his right foot and absorbs the side-to-side contact with VanVleet (TOR) as the screen is set.
Irving's (BKN) off-arm comes forward slightly and marginal contact occurs with VanVleet's (TOR) right shoulder/arm as VanVleet's momentum continues to carry him forward.
Irving (BKN) gathers the ball on his right foot and takes two steps before coming to a stop on the perimeter.
VanVleet (TOR) legally contests Irving's (BKN) jump shot attempt.
